description: City: RiversideTaste our original, authentic flavor! Inland Empire taco cart servicing the greater LA area.Offering mobile taco catering for all types of events, parties, sports tournaments, corporate gatherings, graduations, quinceanera's, etc. This is the most delicious taco experience you will have this side of the border...Guaranteed!We offer "fresh off the grill"  Jalisco style tacos, which include all the fixings:OnionsCilantroGuacamoleRed and Green Salsa (hot or mild)LemonsRadishes We prepare marinated Beef, Chicken and Pork.
name: Jalisco's Mobile Taco Grill
